<td>5</td>
<td align="left"><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/United_Kingdom" title="United Kingdom"><img alt="Flag of the United Kingdom" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ae/Flag_of_the_United_Kingdom.svg/22px-Flag_of_the_United_Kingdom.svg.png" width="22" height="11" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Royal_Bank_of_Scotland" title="Royal Bank of Scotland">Royal Bank of Scotland</a></td>
<td align="right">7.30%</td>
